  - smoke-test /forgot-password + /reset-password/[token] — public routes, no credentials needed (Phase 7 #4 carryover). With the 24h cap live, manual /forgot-password smoke for the same email is limited to 5 requests per 24h — use distinct emails or trust test assertions
