  - NEW from #8e: smoke-test Socket.IO handshake. (1) start dev env with SOCKET_PORT=43515; (2) `curl http://localhost:43515/socket.io/` returns Socket.IO handshake page; (3) browser session in /app connects to ws://localhost:43515 + console logs no errors; (4) trigger session invalidation in another tab (sign out, or admin disables user) → wait ≤60s → verify the connected socket receives `session:invalidated` event and disconnects.
